{"id":80,"date":"2020-10-01T08:26:24","date_gmt":"2020-10-01T08:26:24","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/?page_id=80"},"modified":"2024-01-08T14:09:54","modified_gmt":"2024-01-08T14:09:54","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"Scoutmasters&#8217; Minutes"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-2486197b\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns alignfull has-1-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-equal-layout has-vertical-center\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-fe550b0c\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<h1 id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-a93999eb\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-a93999eb\">Scoutmasters&#8217; minutes<\/h1>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-94dec1f4\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns alignfull has-1-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-equal-layout has-vertical-flex-start has-light-bg\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-7b0444df\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<section id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-1727ab75\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns has-2-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-collapsedRows-layout has-vertical-center has-reverse-columns-mobile has-light-bg\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-28d31c74\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-0690b8b5\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-0690b8b5\"><strong>HOW WE STARTED<\/strong><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\">What I know in 60 seconds<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">It is a privilege to serve as the Scoutmaster for Troop 156 Boys, steeped in rich history in Ramstein. With three sons in the troop, I am fully dedicated to mentoring, guiding youth by the principles of the Scout Oath and Law, and supporting them as they evolve into leaders who make moral and ethical choices in their lives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Supported by a strong and passionate committee, we foster a scout-led troop. Our mission is simple: train them, trust them, let them lead\u2014the essence of Lord Baden-Powell&#8217;s original vision for scouting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">YIS, <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Truett Sanchez, Scoutmaster <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Troop 156 Boys<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"mailto:ramsteinscouts156@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ramsteinscouts156@gmail.com<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-f968dc4e\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image ticss-0c5bbe67\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/droppedImage.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163 lazyload\" style=\"width:433px;height:544px\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"378\" height=\"475\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/droppedImage.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163 lazyload\" style=\"width:433px;height:544px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/droppedImage.jpg 378w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/droppedImage-239x300.jpg 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 378px) 100vw, 378px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/folder-cover-image_logo_SBBC-BC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-295 lazyload\" style=\"width:432px;height:395px\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"675\" height=\"619\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/folder-cover-image_logo_SBBC-BC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-295 lazyload\" style=\"width:432px;height:395px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/folder-cover-image_logo_SBBC-BC.jpg 675w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/folder-cover-image_logo_SBBC-BC-300x275.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/section>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background\" style=\"background-color:#f8f4e4\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:5vw;line-height:1.1\"><strong>Scouting builds CHARACTER<\/strong> and instills VALUES for a LIFETIME.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:5px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-medium-font-size is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.38%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Setting a course for adventure.<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Scouts BSA is the traditional Scouting experience where youth ages 11-17 can have amazing adventures in the great outdoors, develop a love of service by volunteering in their community, boost leadership skills through fun and exciting challenges, and create memories of a lifetime!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>For more than 100 years, Scouts BSA has helped create generations of leaders and outstanding citizens by providing young people with the opportunity to explore their interests, serve their communities, and discover new talents through youth-led activities like hiking, camping, and volunteering!<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Alpine-High-Adventure2-edited.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-351 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Alpine-High-Adventure2-edited.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-351 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Alpine-High-Adventure2-edited.jpg 500w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Alpine-High-Adventure2-edited-188x300.jpg 188w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.62%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SERVICE<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Scouting builds leaders. Former Scouts serve on the boards of global corporations, walk the halls of the White House, and have been known to go hiking on the moon occasionally. Life lessons learned in Scouting will help all of its members make good decisions throughout life.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Leadership development<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>As leaders, Scouts are taught to listen carefully to the ideas of their peers, to be fair, flexible, and organized, to follow up on assignments, to delegate when necessary, be quick to encourage or praise for a job well done, to know when to ask for help, to accept criticism as a gift, and most of all, to have fun.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PERSONAL GROWTH<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-medium-font-size\"><strong>The Scout slogan is Do a Good Turn Daily. That means doing something to help others each day without expecting anything in return. It implies that Scouts learn to do their part in caring for the community and the environment.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Now-this-is-fun.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-350 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Now-this-is-fun.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-350 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Now-this-is-fun.jpg 800w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Now-this-is-fun-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Now-this-is-fun-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-00fbcfb3\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns has-1-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-equal-layout has-vertical-unset\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-81d947be\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background has-medium-font-size\" style=\"background-color:#f2f0e9\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:70px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:38px;line-height:1.1\"><strong>Advancements and Awards<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\"\/>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Rub-a-dub-tub12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-352 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"522\" height=\"800\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Rub-a-dub-tub12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-352 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Rub-a-dub-tub12.jpg 522w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Rub-a-dub-tub12-196x300.jpg 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 522px) 100vw, 522px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-medium-font-size is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Advancement is the Scouts BSA method of promoting and encouraging ongoing involvement and commitment to keep youth engaged in the adventure! Scouts progress from rank to rank as they work their way up to Eagle Scout.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">MERIT BADGES<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\"><strong> Learn about sports, crafts, science, trades, business, and future careers as you earn merit badges. There are over 135 merit badges covering a variety of subjects. From archery and wilderness survival to environmental science and robotics to cooking and theater, there&#8217;s something for everyone!<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-medium-font-size is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">EAGLE SCOUT<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>The Eagle Scout award is the highest rank available. It is a prestigious and rewarding accomplishment known for the amount of work and dedication required to achieve it. Start your journey today!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-349 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-349 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/AC6I2410_photo_SBBC-1-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Scouting builds CHARACTER and instills VALUES for a LIFETIME. Setting a course for adventure. Scouts BSA is the traditional Scouting experience where youth ages 11-17 can have amazing adventures in the great outdoors, develop a love of service by volunteering in their community, boost leadership skills through fun and exciting challenges, and create memories of&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/ramsteinboyscouts.com\/about\/\" class=\"\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read More &raquo;<span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Scoutmasters&#8217; Minutes<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-templates\/template-pagebuilder-full-width.php","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"neve_meta_sidebar":"full-width","neve_meta_container":"","neve_meta_enable_content_width":"on","neve_meta_content_width":100,"neve_meta_title_alignment":